Have been writing this all week. It felt nice to let it form itself over time. The past couple of months I‚Äôve been taking stock of my mental health and I‚Äôm so glad I have because I was heading to a horrible burn-out. The past 3 years or so have brought about some incredibly damaging things to my life and it seems to happen one after the other. Watching people who look like me being murdered since I was 7 and seeing it happen almost daily only exacerbated that while still having to work at a decreased pay-rate/keeping a roof over my head).
I‚Äôve had to fake myself out of a lot of funk and that‚Äôs not healthy.
On the other side, another part of me has grown more dedicated to living an honest life. And I love that.

More to say but maybe I‚Äôll write about it üòâ

Take care of yourself.. the universe only made one!

